WEBVTT

00:01.397 --> 00:03.205
So this is what it's come to.

00:04.671 --> 00:07.435
Human sardines packing into tiny frames,...

00:08.573 --> 00:11.283
...carrying around sticks like cave people,...

00:12.165 --> 00:14.799
...trying anything to fit in everything.

00:15.413 --> 00:17.901
You can keep struggling to get everyone in your shot,...

00:19.055 --> 00:22.497
...or you can change the way you take selfies.

00:24.769 --> 00:27.205
The Samsung Galaxy S6 and S6 Edge,...

00:27.333 --> 00:29.625
...with a wide-angle and hi-res selfie camera.

